<p><a name="Sources" id="Sources"></a></p>
<h2><span class="editsection">[<a href="/w/index.php?title=Truman_Capote&amp;action=edit&amp;section=22" title="Edit section: Sources">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline">Sources</span></h2>
